data.description: Updated brick fron home close to I-85/GA-316, schools, shops & restaurants. Vaulted ceiling and brick fireplace in living room. Hardwood floors on main and stairs. Kitchen has beautiful granite countertops, rolling island, s/steel appliances, farmhouse apron fron sink, touchless faucet, and solid wood cabinets with spice racks & pull-out trash. Large family/sun room at rear has low-e French door with built-in blinds and opens out to a brick patio and large backyard. Master bedroom is on main floor and has 2 walk-in closets and spacious bathroom with beautiful shower & jacuzzi. Home also features a loft for home office/gym/additional sleeping area, brand new HVAC, newer roof, water heater and low-e double-hung windows, recently installed one-piece high efficiency dual flush toilets, and an external storage unit. You'll love this beautiful home!
